&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a class="csaf-accordion-toggle" href="#"&gt;CVE-2026-20902&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="csaf-accordion-content"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An OS Command injection vulnerability exists in XWEB Pro version 1.12.1 and prior, enabling an authenticated attacker to achieve remote code execution on the system by injecting malicious input into the map filename field during the map upload action of the parameters route.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-20902"&gt;View CVE Details&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
