&lt;div class="csaf-accordion-content"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Frick Controls Quantum HD contains a vulnerability that allows an unauthenticated attacker to execute arbitrary code on the affected device, leading to full system compromise.&lt;/p&gt;
